肖褍薪泻褑懈褟 block_extsyncdoc_run_process_command_result_update(context, block_context, command, result, objects)
	connection_uuid = context.operation.小胁芯泄褋褌胁芯("connection_uuid");
	
	袝褋谢懈 薪械 command.Data.data.小胁芯泄褋褌胁芯("袠写袠小") 袠 result.小胁芯泄褋褌胁芯("袠写袠小") 孝芯谐写邪
